Unique ID: String identifier unique trough the document to handle updates
Title: String value
Categories: String value of comma separated categories (you can specify another separator - I just need a symbol to split the data on import)
Tags: String value of comma separated tags (you can specify another separator - I just need a symbol to split the data on import)
Effective Date: Date or string value to fit specific format mm/dd/YY
Updated Date: Date or string value to fit specific format mm/dd/YY
